```troff
.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "2025-11-11" "v1.0" "Simple Shell Manual"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple command line interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ./hsh
.SH DESCRIPTION
simple_shell is a minimal UNIX shell written in C. It can execute commands with absolute or relative paths, search for commands in the PATH, and supports built-in commands such as env and exit.
.SH USAGE
Run the shell:

$ ./hsh

Then type commands:

$ ls -l
$ env
$ /bin/ls
$ exit
.SH AUTHORS
Shahad Alsaneea
Rahaf Alhareti
